	(text "Possible extension for pull-up resistors, I will not install them because the length of the power cable will be max. 2 m. \nIf you have more, I recommend installing them for a more stable I2C signal. \nThe main board already has pull-up resistors, so you only need to add these two for the entire sensor board if you are going to run longer distances."
